        "educational_objectives": [
          "Apply theoretical and practical knowledge in Electronics, Communication, and emerging areas such as AI, IoT, and intelligent systems to solve engineering problems.",
          "Pursue higher education, research, or professional advancement in engineering or management fields with adaptability to technological evolution.",
          "Demonstrate leadership, professionalism, and teamwork in multidisciplinary environments for national and global development."
        ],
        "specific_outcomes": [
          "Demonstrate analytical, problem-solving, and design skills in analog/digital circuits, communication systems, signal processing, VLSI, and embedded systems.",
